articles.title: Miss Universe Credits Filipino-Texas Family for Her Crown - Voice of America - VOA News
articles.description: R'Bonney Gabriel, who is also Miss USA, said her 'big, loud and fun' clan along with the more reserved side of her family helped shape her success
articles.content:
New York  R'Bonney Gabriel is the first Filipina American to wear the Miss Universe crown in the pageant's seven-decade history and, at 28, the oldest entrant ever crowned.
